title: NBA 2k11 roster update [ April, 18th, 2012]
description:
Here's the last and final release. A roster update for NBA 2k11 PC version. Rosters all accurate as of the trade deadline, march,15,2012. 

 6 Rookies Added as requested by 2k players:

-Kyrie Irving

-Kemba Walker

-Norris Cole

-Derrick Williams

-Tristan Thompson

-Bismack Biyombo


( sorry if i didn't include your teams' rookie(s) )


**Just minor changes, involving player pick-ups by teams**



Please seed 1:1 ratio so the file can last and others can enjoy it.
